OL,3,CPublic outcry at 'embarrassing'
OL,4,Cmisspelt road sign
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey have labelled the
OL,7,Fmisspelling of a popular coastal area
OL,8,Fon a road sign as "embarrassing".
OL,10,FLa Pulente in St Ouen is often talked
OL,11,Fabout for its breathtaking views of St
OL,12,FOuen's Bay and walking routes, but
OL,13,Finstead, comments centred around an
OL,14,Funfortunate typo in the printing of a
OL,15,Fnew sign.
OL,17,FIt is situated on Mont Pinel, at the
OL,18,Fjunction with Route de L'Etacq, which
OL,19,Fleads down to the Bay, with a rogue
OL,20,Fletter 'a' meaning people were
OL,21,Fdirected to 'La Paulente'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
