OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772629888
OL,3,CPublic outcry at 'embarrassing'
OL,4,Cmisspelt road sign
OL,6,FA picture was posted on social media
OL,7,Fand widely ridiculed, with previous
OL,8,Fexamples of local sign typos also
OL,9,Fshared.
OL,11,F"So embarrassing," one user said. "It
OL,12,Fjust needs to be double-checked by
OL,13,Fsomeone, which takes seconds. Why
OL,14,Faren't they doing this?"
OL,16,FAnother added: "One job, just one job."
OL,18,FA third questioned: "Does anybody
OL,19,Fproofread these days?"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772629888
OL,3,CPublic outcry at 'embarrassing'
OL,4,Cmisspelt road sign
OL,6,FHowever, some did see the funny side
OL,7,Fof the mishap.
OL,9,FOne cheeky commenter asked: "Was the
OL,10,Fsign left behind by the Bergerac film
OL,11,Fcrew?"
OL,13,FAnother chimed: "Lucky St Ouen was
OL,14,Fcorrect?"
OL,16,FOthers were more sympathetic about the
OL,17,Fblunder, as one user stated: "Mistakes
OL,18,Fhappen."
OL,20,FThe sign has since been corrected.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
